ClassDiagramEdges  : Abstraction | Dependency | Association | ElementImport | InterfaceRealization | Generalization | PackageImport | PackageMerge | Realization | Substitution | Usage ;
SlotDefiningFeature  : Property | Class | Interface ;
ActivityDiagramElements  : ActivityDiagramNodes | ActivityDiagramEdges ;
